cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically 3D object detection and pose estimation from RGB data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves training deep neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of synthetic data for training suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category. The application of the method to robotics tasks suggests cs.RO (Robotics and Control) as a likely category. Finally, the use of 3D models and their instances suggests cs.GR (Graphics) as a possible category.
